{"tid":1790144,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"要襯住今次機會 發展離岸星火+海外黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-12-19T18:42:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T00:45:45.000Z","uid":95138,"like":111,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"5db0075809d0861e9c3736f1bcc481325c74db55","tid":1790144,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:42:34.000Z","msg":"就算再開過個戶口 擺錢喺香港都唔再安全<br />\n銀行隨時可以話AML (Anti Money Laundering) 再停星火/其他組織嘅戶口<br />\n政府/黑警亦可以向法庭申請凍結資產<br />\n<br />\n經過今次 我地應該大規模將資產轉移到海外<br />\n首選一D最反共嘅國家 例如台灣、美國<br />\n相關交易全部喺海外完成 唔經香港銀行手，亦都唔需要有香港戶口<br />\n捐錢一樣用VISA/Master搞掂，方便快捷<br />\n<br />\n另外可以擴展黃色經濟圈到海外<br />\n支援逃亡義士嘅生計（黃國桐律師已經搞緊台灣戰線）<br />\n而當地支持我地嘅人，都可以好方便地幫襯或者捐款<br />\n<br />\n其實7000萬已經可以搞到規模唔細嘅生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713bf940c804e14de18f20d8c84a152f57145727","tid":1790144,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=cb19abd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=fea6831e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a><br />\n<br />\n請推po<br />\n<br />\n【核彈】呢個方法可以防水炮車【行動po求推】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab941ecb132c2ffc1942c3cff0b8eab70939339c","tid":1790144,"uid":95138,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:45:30.000Z","msg":"另外想講 今次大貓絕對唔係無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n19/11滙豐高層入完港澳辦 21/11就停星火戶口<br />\n今日相信因為星火手足用個人戶口處理筆錢，所以俾黑警屈洗黑錢，兼凍結7000萬資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n舊錢有排都拎唔返"},{"pid":"ba6ab5c4df1810182f30f2a5b5c77187926a5483","tid":1790144,"uid":95138,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T18:47:42.000Z","msg":"首選 台灣美國<br />\n次選 日本韓國<br />\n<br />\n但都要小心中共喺當地嘅滲透<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3e79f62c8fb206963a0cd95a7f2ee7cfa5cdb8","tid":1790144,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:00:45.000Z","msg":"大家有冇建議 做咩行業咁<br />\n以下開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75370e9a624c8947d2fe9de28334d7d28ead326f","tid":1790144,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:06:43.000Z","msg":"希望攬炒巴團隊可以幫手<br />\n佢地好多外國connection<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b21e0bb91ed1d47abad3e3dd408e6b20c7768b1","tid":1790144,"uid":140793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:10:37.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2421aa78b09cde945060afcb20b94e30605ee1c7","tid":1790144,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:15:23.000Z","msg":"希望大家幫手brain storm下<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0efdadb40689294439b3bbddca19757249d6b246","tid":1790144,"uid":66729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:18:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b520e1d0eac9405faa9de67836205cfeeaed6731","tid":1790144,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T19:20:56.000Z","msg":"喺台灣開始